// p0 = haploid population
// p1 = diploid population

// shadie DEFINITIONS
// p0 = haploid population
// p1 = diploid population
// >2000000 = male gametophyte (1N)
// <2000000 = female gametophyte (1N)
// 2 = gametophyte clones (1N)
// 3 = sporophyte (2N)
// >1M- tmp tags
